## Consistency Check

### What happened

Flow could not run the consistency check yet.

### Why Flow stopped

`tasks.md` does not exist yet. Flow needs it before it can compare the spec and task list.

### What to fix

Run `/flow-plan` to create `tasks.md`, then run the command again.

### Nothing was changed automatically

Flow did not close verification, close the change, or change these planning files.

### Next command

`/flow-plan`
